description:
My place is close to Taverna Kyclades, Watawa Sushi, MP Taverna, The Bonnie... The greatest cultural diversity in NYC . 
You’ll love my place because of the relaxed Astoria vibe; you are steps from NYC.
. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.

hosts.about:
Holler, I'm Kevin!
I've lived in NYC, various parts, for the past 10 years. I am one of those NYC slashers. 
Ok... I'll clarify. I am an Actor/Singer/Designer/Artist/Waiter/DomesticGoddess. Ok, the last one might be a bit much, but you get my point. I enjoying living life to the fullest and making every bit as creative as possible along the way. I'm not just one of the art guys, I did grow up outside Philly playing a sport every season and consider myself well rounded. 
Alright, thats it about me for now. I don't want to reveal to much, what will we talk about?
